(252643, 8418, 252603, 'Wolf Hunter', 3441, '', 1330981780, 'The term Effective Range is not related to length of the barrel. It is a term used to express the comparison between "Maximum Range  and Effective Range".\nA projectile of a bullet has to travel a specified distance depending on the velocity,grains,caliber & type of bullet and the barrel of length.This travel of bullets terminates  when projectile loses its power and drops due to gravity at a specific point. So this is the Maximum range of bullet where as Effective Range of bullet  is defined when a projectile is potent to penetrate an object,with no lose of velocity and speed.', 1, 0, '182.178.60.110', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
