(252966, 3553, 221997, 'Huzaifa', 5467, '', 1331094229, '[QUOTE=jeesjee;221997]For 144 permit you need following things\n\n1. Write an Application for 144 Permit. \n2. Three (3) Passport Size Photos\n3. Photo Copy of your License.\n4. Photo Copy of your CNIC\n\nif you have all theses things now goto Home Department Arms Section then goto SO Office (Mr. Pir Bux) is (SO) you only need his signature on your application then goto khalid bhai room and submit your application with all papers and collect your permit after 3 working days.\n\nyou only need source to reach SO for signature otherwise there is nothing and its 100% Free of cost .\n\nApplication is just a formality kay why u want 144 permit u just write that u want it for carry purpose or ager chahein to bahir jo log bethay hotey hain wo likh detay hain in just Rs. 20/-......[/QUOTE]\n\n Nice information but I think source ke zaroorat nahi hai. Direct go to Section officer''s room  he is very nice person i have converted my two licenses from Provincial to All Pakistan & he signed my both applications without any hurdle.', 1, 1, '113.203.187.106', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
